snippet.title: Pray For America (Barron Trump Singing)
snippet.description:
Pray For America

Check us out on Spotify! https://open.spotify.com/album/3y1CZVxPBVqYl2ljdNVWno?si=lLRWLYbeQcuXD9TQDeKi7A

⬇️⬇️⬇️ Watch more videos below! ⬇️⬇️⬇️
https://youtu.be/WBHJZs8ZeFQ
https://youtu.be/GAdihLnAiXk
https://youtu.be/SZZW8YMZlMg?si=kP7ZE5s5fhhjjpX2
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hq_JjAodbY0

Lyrics:
Verse 1:
Verse 1
Times are tough, the world’s on edge,
Wars and worries, walking the ledge.
Tariffs rise, the tensions grow,
But through it all, one thing I know.

Pre-Chorus
God is greater, He’s in control,
Through every trial, He holds our soul.
So on my knees, I humbly stay,
Lifting my country when I pray.

Chorus
Pray for America, strong and free,
God’s light shining for all to see.
Through the storms, through the fight,
We stand in faith, we stand in light.

Verse 2
Nations clash, the headlines scream,
Ukraine’s in battle, Russia’s extreme.
Leaders talk, but hearts must turn,
Only through God can peace return.

Pre-Chorus
God is greater, He’s in control,
Through every trial, He holds our soul.
So on my knees, I humbly stay,
Lifting my country when I pray.

Chorus
Pray for America, strong and free,
God’s light shining for all to see.
Through the storms, through the fight,
We stand in faith, we stand in light.

Bridge
Through every tariff, every test,
God still loves, His way is best.
Hold the line, don’t lose sight,
Hope will rise in morning’s light.

Chorus
Pray for America, strong and free,
God’s light shining for all to see.
Through the storms, through the fight,
We stand in faith, we stand in light.

Outro
So I pray, I believe, I trust His plan,
God still reigns over this land.
With hands together, voices high,
America, we lift you to the sky.
